..and they ran away in horror.

1040
01:40:13,956 --> 01:40:19,662
In my loneliness, I decided that if I could not
inspire love, which was my deepest hope,...

1041
01:40:20,797 --> 01:40:23,003
..I would instead cause fear!

1042
01:40:25,135 --> 01:40:27,211
I live...

1043
01:40:28,472 --> 01:40:33,763
..because this poor, half-crazed genius
has given me life.

1044
01:40:34,311 --> 01:40:36,387
He alone held an image of me...

1045
01:40:36,480 --> 01:40:38,556
..as something beautiful.

1046
01:40:39,275 --> 01:40:41,184
And then,...

1047
01:40:41,277 --> 01:40:45,144
..when it would have been easy enough
to stay out of danger,...

1048
01:40:45,615 --> 01:40:48,699
..he used his own body as a guinea pig...

1049
01:40:48,785 --> 01:40:50,861
..to give me a calmer brain...

1050
01:40:52,539 --> 01:40:58,708
..and a... somewhat more... sophisticated way
of expressing myself.

1051
01:40:59,880 --> 01:41:03,747
Well, this is, of course,
an entirely different situation.

1052
01:41:04,426 --> 01:41:06,751
As the leader of this community,...

1053
01:41:07,221 --> 01:41:10,969
..may I be the first to offer you my hand...

1054
01:41:11,684 --> 01:41:13,760
..in friendship.

1055
01:41:19,776 --> 01:41:22,183
- Thank you.
- You are entirely welcome.

1056
01:41:22,279 --> 01:41:27,237
Und now let us all go to my house
for a little sponge cake und a little wine...

1057
01:41:28,535 --> 01:41:30,611
..und... Shit!

1058
01:41:33,124 --> 01:41:35,200
To the lumberyard!

1059
01:41:58,984 --> 01:42:01,605
Hello, Mrs Frankenstein.

1060
01:42:02,321 --> 01:42:05,606
Mrs Frankenstein! What a beautiful name!

1061
01:42:05,700 --> 01:42:07,408
Oh, darling!

1062
01:42:07,493 --> 01:42:09,569
Hold on to your hat.

1063
01:42:10,997 --> 01:42:11,945
What?

1064
01:42:12,040 --> 01:42:15,076
I'll be right back.

1065
01:42:29,308 --> 01:42:31,929
I'm holding on to it, darling!

1066
01:42:32,774 --> 01:42:35,068
Just a few more seconds!

1067
01:43:15,566 --> 01:43:19,610
Honey! Honey, I hope you didn't find
Daddy's little part too boring.

1068
01:43:19,695 --> 01:43:23,277
I mean, he did it just for you
and he meant so well. Say you liked it.

1069
01:43:24,575 --> 01:43:26,651
Honey, did you see?

1070
01:43:26,744 --> 01:43:30,243
I put a special hamper in the bathroom
just for your shirts...

1071
01:43:30,331 --> 01:43:33,664
..and the other one is just for socks
and poo-poo undies.

1072
01:43:33,752 --> 01:43:35,246
Here I come!

1073
01:44:04,367 --> 01:44:06,443
The feeling is mutual.

1074
01:44:09,164 --> 01:44:11,240
You know, it's a puzzlement.

1075
01:44:11,333 --> 01:44:15,829
There's something I've always wanted
to ask you about that operation.

1076
01:44:15,921 --> 01:44:18,127
You know in the transference part...

1077
01:44:18,215 --> 01:44:23,719
The monster got part of your wonderful brain,
but what did you ever get from him?

